{"id": "art-16", "label": "Art. 16", "title": "Art. 16", "slug": "art-16", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1857951828\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1398\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1857951828\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 16 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1290085834\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1397\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1290085834\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Contractul individual de munc&#259; se încheie în baza\nconsim&#355;&#259;mântului p&#259;r&#355;ilor, în form&#259; scris&#259;, în\nlimba român&#259;, cel târziu în ziua anterioar&#259; începerii\nactivit&#259;&#355;ii de c&#259;tre salariat. Obliga&#355;ia de încheiere a\ncontractului individual de munc&#259; în form&#259; scris&#259; revine\nangajatorului.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_464054161\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1396\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_464054161\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>1</sup>)P&#259;r&#355;ile pot opta s&#259; utilizeze\nla încheierea, modificarea, suspendarea sau, dup&#259; caz, la încetarea\ncontractului individual de munc&#259; semn&#259;tura electronic&#259;\navansat&#259; sau semn&#259;tura electronic&#259; calificat&#259;.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1030160331\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1395\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1030160331\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>2</sup>)Angajatorul poate opta pentru utilizarea\nsemn&#259;turii electronice, semn&#259;turii electronice avansate sau\nsemn&#259;turii electronice calificate ori a sigiliului electronic al\nangajatorului, pentru întocmirea tuturor înscrisurilor/documentelor din domeniul\nrela&#355;iilor de munc&#259; rezultate la încheierea contractului individual\nde munc&#259;, pe parcursul execut&#259;rii acestuia sau la încetarea\ncontractului individual de munc&#259;, în condi&#355;iile stabilite prin\nregulamentul intern &#351;i/sau contractul colectiv de munc&#259; aplicabil,\npotrivit legii.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_582492633\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1394\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_582492633\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>3</sup>)Contractele individuale de munc&#259;\n&#351;i actele adi&#355;ionale încheiate prin utilizarea semn&#259;turii\nelectronice avansate sau semn&#259;turii electronice calificate, precum &#351;i\nînscrisurile/documentele din domeniul rela&#355;iilor de munc&#259; se\narhiveaz&#259; de c&#259;tre angajator cu respectarea prevederilor Legii\nArhivelor Na&#355;ionale nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>16/1996</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, republicat&#259;, &#351;i ale Legii nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>135/2007</span><span style='color:black'> privind\narhivarea documentelor în form&#259; electronic&#259;, republicat&#259;,\n&#351;i vor fi puse la dispozi&#355;ia organelor de control competente, la\nsolicitarea acestora.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_589300420\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1393\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_589300420\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>4</sup>)[textul din Art. 16, alin. (1^4) din titlul\nII, capitolul I a fost abrogat la 25-iul-2021 de </span><span style='color:\n#1B1B1B'>Art. 1, punctul 3. din Legea 208/2021</span><span style='color:black'>]</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_446930123\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1392\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_446930123\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>5</sup>)[textul din Art. 16, alin. (1^5) din titlul\nII, capitolul I a fost abrogat la 25-iul-2021 de </span><span style='color:\n#1B1B1B'>Art. 1, punctul 3. din Legea 208/2021</span><span style='color:black'>]</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1071685004\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1391\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1071685004\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>6</sup>)Angajatorul nu poate obliga persoana\nselectat&#259; în vederea angaj&#259;rii ori, dup&#259; caz, salariatul s&#259;\nutilizeze semn&#259;tura electronic&#259; avansat&#259; sau semn&#259;tura\nelectronic&#259; calificat&#259;, la încheierea, modificarea, suspendarea sau,\ndup&#259; caz, la încetarea contractului individual de munc&#259;.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_734343092\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1390\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_734343092\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>7</sup>)La încheierea, modificarea, suspendarea sau,\ndup&#259; caz, la încetarea contractului individual de munc&#259;,\np&#259;r&#355;ile trebuie s&#259; utilizeze acela&#351;i tip de\nsemn&#259;tur&#259;, respectiv semn&#259;tura olograf&#259; sau semn&#259;tura\nelectronic&#259;, în condi&#355;iile prezentei legi.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1534745447\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1389\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1534745447\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>8</sup>)Organele de control competente au\nobliga&#355;ia de a accepta, pentru verificare &#351;i control, contractele\nindividuale de munc&#259; &#351;i actele adi&#355;ionale, precum &#351;i\nînscrisurile/documentele din domeniul rela&#355;iilor de munc&#259;/securit&#259;&#355;ii\n&#351;i s&#259;n&#259;t&#259;&#355;ii în munc&#259; încheiate în format\nelectronic, cu semn&#259;tura electronic&#259;, potrivit legii, f&#259;r&#259;\na le solicita &#351;i în format letric. La solicitarea acestora, documentele\nîncheiate cu semn&#259;tura electronic&#259; pot fi transmise în format\nelectronic &#351;i anterior efectu&#259;rii controlului.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2094909681\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1388\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2094909681\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Anterior începerii activit&#259;&#355;ii, contractul\nindividual de munc&#259; se înregistreaz&#259; în registrul general de\neviden&#355;&#259; a salaria&#355;ilor, care se transmite inspectoratului\nteritorial de munc&#259; cel târziu în ziua anterioar&#259; începerii\nactivit&#259;&#355;ii.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1707860084\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1387\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1707860084\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Angajatorul este obligat ca, anterior începerii\nactivit&#259;&#355;ii, s&#259; înmâneze salariatului un exemplar din contractul\nindividual de munc&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_164257330\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1386\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_164257330\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Angajatorul este obligat s&#259; p&#259;streze la locul\nde munc&#259; o copie a contractului individual de munc&#259; pentru\nsalaria&#355;ii care presteaz&#259; activitate în acel loc.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1196448049\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1385\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1196448049\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Munca prestat&#259; în temeiul unui contract individual\nde munc&#259; constituie vechime în munc&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_56767155\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1384\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_56767155\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Absen&#355;ele nemotivate &#351;i concediile\nf&#259;r&#259; plat&#259; se scad din vechimea în munc&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1819864565\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1383\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1819864565\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Fac excep&#355;ie de la prevederile alin. (6) concediile\npentru formare profesional&#259; f&#259;r&#259; plat&#259;, acordate în\ncondi&#355;iile art. 155 &#351;i 156.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}